===Etymology===
A reference to a [[wooden]] [[ship#Noun|ship]] being [[pound#Verb|pounded]] [[heavily]] in [[stormy]] [[sea]]s to the extent that its [[timber]]s [[shake#Verb|shake]], causing the [[sailor]]s on board [[awe#Noun|awe]] and [[fear#Noun|fear]].

